{
  "chapter": 61,
  "chapter_summary": "第六十一回 承诺。吕凤先本欲杀李寻欢，却在其真诚目光中感受到友情的光辉，最终放弃杀意。李寻欢趁机请求吕凤先帮他做一件事——除掉令阿飞沉沦的林仙儿。吕凤先被李寻欢的坦诚打动，答应前往。阿飞醒来发现李寻欢在病痛中沉睡，不忍惊动，独自出门。在豆浆铺中，阿飞先后看到\"说书先生\"祖孙、荆无命和上官飞三人先后经过。荆无命曾以剑击败阿飞，令其几乎沉沦，阿飞心生战意。上官飞似在暗中追踪荆无命，阿飞也尾随而去，三人先后消失在土山之后。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "speaker_name": "吕凤先",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你的意思是说，你能为他死，他也会为你死，是不是？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "speaker_name": "吕凤先",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "但你已算准了我不会杀你，至少不会在这种情况下杀你，是不是？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "speaker_name": "吕凤先",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我的确不会杀你……你可知道是为了什么？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "speaker_name": "吕凤先",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "因为我要你永远欠着我的，永远觉得我对你有恩……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "speaker_name": "吕凤先",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "因为我若要杀你，以后还有机会，但这种机会以后只怕永远不会再有了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "text": "你还有机会。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "speaker_name": "吕凤先",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "text": "我还要求你做一件事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "speaker_name": "吕凤先",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你第一次交易还未付出代价，就想要我做第二件事了？这算是什么样的交易？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "text": "这不是交易，是我求你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "speaker_name": "吕凤先",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "既然不是交易，我为何要答应？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "text": "因为这是我求你的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "speaker_name": "吕凤先",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "别人都说李寻欢从不求人，今日居然肯来求我，看来我的面子倒不小。",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "text": "我既已欠了你的，再多欠些又何妨？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "speaker_name": "吕凤先",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "有人说，学做生意最大的学问就是要懂得如何欠帐，看来你本该去做生意的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 71
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "text": "你肯答应？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "speaker_name": "吕凤先",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "至少我现在还未想出拒绝的法子，你趁此机会，赶快说吧。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 77
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "speaker_name": "吕凤先",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "只不过短短两年，他怎会改变得如此多？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "text": "只因他不幸遇上了一个人。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "speaker_name": "吕凤先",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "女人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "text": "自然是女人，世上也许只有女人才能改变男人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "speaker_name": "吕凤先",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "他不是改变，而是堕落，一个男人为了女人而堕落，这种人非但不值得同情，而且愚蠢得可笑。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 101
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "text": "你说得也许不错，只因你还未遇到过那样的女人。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 105
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "speaker_name": "吕凤先",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我遇见了又如何？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "text": "你若遇见了她，说不定也许变得和阿飞一样的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "speaker_name": "吕凤先",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你以为我也是个没见过女人的小伙子？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "text": "你也许见过各式各样的女人，可是她……她却绝对和别的女人不同。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 115
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "speaker_name": "吕凤先",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "text": "曾经有个人将她形容得很好……她看来如仙子，却专门带男人下地狱。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 121
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "speaker_name": "吕凤先",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我已知道你说的是谁了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "text": "你本该猜到的，因为世上只有她这么一个女人，也幸好只有一个，否则只怕大多数男人都已活不下去。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 127
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "speaker_name": "吕凤先",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "有关这位'天下第一美人'的传说，我的确已听到过不少。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 131
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "text": "阿飞现在总算已振作起来，我不能眼看着他再沉沦下去，所以……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "speaker_name": "吕凤先",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "所以你要我去杀了她？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "text": "我只希望阿飞永远莫要再见到她，因为只要一见到她，阿飞就无法自拔。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 139
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "speaker_name": "吕凤先",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你本可自己动手的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "text": "只是我不能。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "speaker_name": "吕凤先",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "text": "因为阿飞若知道了，必将恨我终生。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "speaker_name": "吕凤先",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "他应该明白你这是为他好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "text": "无论多聪明的人，若是陷入情感而不能自拔，都会变成呆子。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 153
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "speaker_name": "吕凤先",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你为何不找别人做这件事？为何要找我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "text": "因为别人纵有力量能杀她，见了她之后只怕也不忍下手，因为……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "text": "我本就很难找到一个我可以去求他的人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 163
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "speaker_name": "吕凤先",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "她在哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "text": "铃铃知道她在哪里，只不过……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "text": "你若想她带你去，只怕并不容易。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 181
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "speaker_name": "吕凤先",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "这倒用不着你担心，我自然有法子的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 61,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    }
  ],
